title: HUMAN EVENTS DAILY: NOV 18 2021 - RITTENHOUSE PROSECUTORS CLAIM TECHNOLOGICAL GLITCH IN EVIDENCE TRANSFER
description:
On today’s episode of Human Events Daily, The Kyle Rittenhouse prosecutors claim there was a technological glitch while transferring evidence, A lawsuit claims the ‘Rust’ script never called for Alec Baldwin’s gun to be fired, The CDC reports the highest number of drug overdoses in one year, and Joy Reid and Elizabeth Warren claim gas prices are up due to a secret plot.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
